	   <tr><td colspan=2>Jeebus!&nbsp;&nbsp;4 skill pts per level???  I already thought we clerics had it tough...<br>I know I am but one of many who play the class and complain about it, but the cleric I play had a role-playing birth back when the US Government was still using card-punch readers.  What I just can't understand about EQ clerics is this:  We are limited to 1h and 2h blunt only, but we are restricted from the best damage dealers in those minute categories as well.  Rated in damage per second, the best 1h blunt clerics can use is ranked #9, while Paladins can wield #4!!!  Shadowknights even have access to better 1h blunts than clerics!  There must be something we can do about this, considering our skill in weapon use never gets as high as the other classes, AND we can't get a 1hander with a damage rating better than 13...<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
